  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released\u00a005/05/2017 10:54 CT (15:55 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.6-PAXpayments-MissingtransactionID\">PAX payments - Missing\u00a0transaction ID</h2><p>There were\u00a0a few edge-cases that could\u00a0cause one of the following errors:</p><ul><li><p>&quot;No transaction ID, could not auto-save the transaction.&quot;</p></li><li><p>&quot;Transaction # is missing for Credit Card transaction.&quot;</p></li></ul><p>We have hardened the system against these edge-case scenarios, which should put the issue to rest.</p>",
